exceptions.exn: Expects a disjunctive pattern with 2 branches.

original: intros. destruct (handleTimeout h st) as [out' [st'' l']]. rewrite H. simpl. inversion_clear H; try discriminate. - inversion H0; try discriminate. split; auto. left. reflexivity. - inversion H0; try discriminate. split; auto. right. reflexivity.
